data.description: SPECTACULAR One-story home, 4 Side Brick, Open floor plan, in Gated section of Sonoma Ranch.   GOURMET Kitchen with a lot of natural light features gas cooking, a farm sink, granite countertop, Stainless Steel Appliances, Island/Breakfast Bar. Pendant lights and built-in Microwave! Lots of cabinets & counter space, walk-in pantry makes this any Gourmets delight. Open to huge living area - great for entertaining.  Gorgeous fireplace to enjoy cooler winter nights. A spacious split master with ensuite - separate granite vanities, separate soaking tub and shower, and upgraded fixtures.  Large Walk-in closet with tons of storage space. BEAUTIFUL plantation shutters in most rooms. All Bedrooms are spacious.  Upgrades include High ceilings (making it light and bright), Designer colors, wood & tile flooring, Ceiling fans, and Architectural niches makes this home special.  Sit and relax or entertain family and friends in the private backyard paradise - Oversized Flagstone patio - partially covered, separate sitting area with fire pit! With still plenty of room to play.   Desirable location in the gated Hills at Sonoma Ranch with community clubhouse, sand volleyball, pool, tennis courts, and sports courts. This GORGEOUS home is close to UTSA, the Rim, Fiesta Texas, and La Cantera Resort! Peaceful, quiet location with easy access to shopping, I-10, and 1604. You got to see it!!! SPA, REFRIGERATOR, WASHER & DRYER do not Convey!!! ***OPEN HOUSE*** Saturday, December 2nd. from 11-3:00 pm.
